src.map

Class HashMap<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • src.map.Map<K,V>
      • src.map.HashMap<K,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Pair<K,V>>, iMap<K,V>

    public class HashMap<K,V>
extends Map<K,V>
    Map implementation using a HashTable of key-value pair. Keys are hashed for fast searching. Elements do not remain in order.
    Since:
    v1.1
